description:
This week on Unqualified Anna and Sim sit down with the hysterical Charlie Day (It's Always Sunny, Horrible Bosses, Fist Fight)! They talk about pranks, rumpology, comic acting vs. dramatic acting and throw down on some Deal Breakers! Then they call Shelby, who finds out a guy that has been flirting with her is married with four children and Katie, who’s not sure what to do when she finds her new boyfriend on Bumble.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
